[Most likely these parks were overlooked because they are probably
not large tourist attractions. However, that does not exclude them
from being in the migratory bird pathway, or subject to birds
introducing disease in those regions. We appreciate Joe helping us
understand where the parks are and their size and importance. - Mod.TG]
